text: Great news! @USNavy has awarded Bath Iron Works a $14.95M contract to create a conceptual design of the FFG(X), a next-generation guided missile frigate. The contract is a huge opportunity for BIW that could lead to enough work to keep the shipyard busy for years. #mepolitics
